ch Interessierten anderer Disziplinen grundlegendes Orientierungswissen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 20. Sep 2019) 4aApplied Linguistics. 4aCommunication. 4aDiscourse Linguistics. 4aKommunikation. 4aLinguistik. 4aSprache. 4aWissen. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aFelder, Ekkehard, eeditor.1 aGardt, Andreas, eeditor.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2014z9783110370270oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831103951670 cprintz978311029568940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110295979423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110295979.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DSPb2014